:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:\r\nRU;mso-fareast-language:RU;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;для комнаты, которые\r\nвам создадут завершенное настроение!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;RU&quot; style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Lato&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:\r\nUK;mso-fareast-language:UK;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-no-proof:yes&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://eklektikstore.com.ua/image/catalog/images/kartinkidljakategorij/tdx-domicil-tischsofa-02(1).jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 779.14px; height: 452.681px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;RU&quot; style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Lato&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:\r\nUK;mso-fareast-language:UK;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-no-proof:yes&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;RU&quot; style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Lato&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:RU;\r\nmso-fareast-language:RU&quot;&gt;Цветочная текстура создает внешний вид прямо в вашей\r\nсобственной столовой!&amp;nbsp;Гости сразу почувствуют себя приветливыми,\r\nстолкнувшись с элементами, вдохновленными деревом, с цветами.&amp;nbsp;Древесина -\r\nодин из наших любимых материалов для использования внутри, потому что это напоминает\r\nсвежий воздух в лесах.&amp;nbsp;Увесистый обеденный стол – из натурального дерева, создает\r\nтрадиционный и современный стиль!&amp;nbsp;Не забывайте о деталях в этой комнате,\r\nпотому что гости заметят.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;RU&quot; style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Lato&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;color:#333333;\r\nmso-ansi-language:UK;mso-fareast-language:UK;mso-no-proof:yes&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Lato&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\ncolor:#333333;mso-ansi-language:UK;mso-fareast-language:UK;mso-no-proof:yes&quot;&gt;Например,\r\nс помощью этих каменых кашпо природа попадает в эту кухню.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Lato&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\ncolor:#333333;mso-ansi-language:RU;mso-fareast-language:RU&quot;&gt; &lt;span lang=&quot;RU&quot;&gt;И\r\nесли вы чувствуете смелость, скрашиваете комнату желтыми&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.themine.com/silk-flowers/jane-seymour-botanicals-sdp264-ylwh-petite-jonquil-in-hampton-pot_g2838095.html&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;RU&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Lato, serif; color: windowtext;&quot;&gt;цветами&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;RU&quot; style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Lato&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:RU;mso-fareast-language:RU&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://eklektikstore.com.ua/image/catalog/images/kartinkidljakategorij/img_1388_s.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 775.164px; height: 517.007px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;RU&quot; style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Lato&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:RU;mso-fareast-language:RU&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;RU&quot; style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Lato&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:RU;mso-fareast-language:RU&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;RU&quot; style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Lato&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;color